s les visites qu’elle organise, la Galerie 2016 s’efforce d’amener et de faire connaître l’art contemporain à différents publics, que ce soit aux enfants, aux étudiants ou aux amateurs d’art en général.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://2016.alessandro-chianese.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/Photo_uni_etudiants.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-14 size-large\" src=\"http://2016.alessandro-chianese.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/Photo_uni_etudiants-1024x455.jpg\" alt=\"Photo_uni_etudiants\" width=\"1024\" height=\"455\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://2016.alessandro-chianese.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/mediation-culturelle.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-15 size-full\" src=\"http://2016.alessandro-chianese.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/mediation-culturelle.jpg\" alt=\" Projet pour les écoles : Jacqueline Meylan\" width=\"842\" height=\"379\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://2016.alessandro-chianese.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/20140307BULCOM1.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-17 size-large\" src=\"http://2016.alessandro-chianese.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/20140307BULCOM1-1024x1021.jpg\" alt=\"20140307BULCOM1\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1021\" /></a>','Médiation culturelle','','publish','open','open','','mediation-culturelle','','','2015-07-23 14:22:46','2015-07-23 13:22:46','',0,'http://2016.alessandro-chianese.com/?page_id=12',0,'page','',0),(13,1,'2015-07-08 16:56:58','2015-07-08 15:56:58','','Mediation_culturelle_Alessandro_Chianese','Projet d\'Alessandro Chianese','inherit','open','open','','mediation_culturelle_alessandro_chianese','','','2015-07-08 16:57:10','2015-07-08 15:57:10','',12,'http://2016.alessandro-chianese.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/Mediation_culturelle_Alessandro_Chianese.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(14,1,'2015-07-08 16:57:46','2015-07-08 15:57:46','','Photo_uni_etudiants','','inherit','open','open','','photo_uni_etudiants','','','2015-07-08 16:57:46','2015-07-08 15:57:46','',12,'http://2016.alessandro-chianese.com/wp-content/