content/uploads/2014/03/Capture-decran-2015-07-23-a-19.37.30.png\" alt=\"Capture d’écran 2015-07-23 à 19.37.30\" width=\"871\" height=\"613\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://2016.alessandro-chianese.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Capture-decran-2015-07-23-a-19.37.20.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-171 size-full\" src=\"http://2016.alessandro-chianese.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Capture-decran-2015-07-23-a-19.37.20.png\" alt=\"Capture d’écran 2015-07-23 à 19.37.20\" width=\"869\" height=\"614\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://2016.alessandro-chianese.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Capture-decran-2015-07-23-a-19.37.03.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-172 size-full\" src=\"http://2016.alessandro-chianese.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Capture-decran-2015-07-23-a-19.37.03.png\" alt=\"Capture d’écran 2015-07-23 à 19.37.03\" width=\"872\" height=\"609\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://2016.alessandro-chianese.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Capture-decran-2015-07-23-a-19.36.32.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-173 size-full\" src=\"http://2016.alessandro-chianese.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Capture-decran-2015-07-23-a-19.36.32.png\" alt=\"Capture d’écran 2015-07-23 à 19.36.32\" width=\"867\" height=\"608\" /></a>\r\n<div data-canvas-width=\"327.6756807650503\">Né en 1946 à Tournai en Belgique, il fera des Études supérieures aux Beaux-Arts de Mons. Il sera nommé professeur de gravure aux Beaux-Arts de Tournai en 1973.</div>\r\n<div data-canvas-width=\"402.38159312370095\">Artiste-intervenant aux Beaux-Arts de Tourcoing et de Douai dès 1980.</div>\r\n<div data-canvas-width=\"188.7286021433611\">Depuis 1973, expositions collectives et personnelles en Belgique, France, Espagne, ex-Yougoslavie, Italie, Suisse, Maroc et en 2004, dans le cadre d’ Europalia, au Musée National de Bucarest.</div>\r\n&nbsp;','Alain Winance','','inherit','open','open','','56-revision-v1','','','2015-08-30 20:02:27','2015-08-30 19:02:27','',56,'http://2016.alessandro-chi