 s’ennuyer, contempler les choses mille fois vues et en redécouvrir enfin l’importance pour nous.\r\n\r\nIl faut s’arrêter à l’essentiel, qui n’est pas le plus spectaculaire, et commencer à effacer…l’image ».\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[pdf-embedder url=\"http://2016.alessandro-chianese.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/accrochages-mars20151.pdf\"]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[pdf-embedder url=\"http://2016.alessandro-chianese.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/Bullcom_N11_20_mars_2015_Nicola_Marcone.pdf\"]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[pdf-embedder url=\"http://2016.alessandro-chianese.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/LExpressMag20150423.pdf\"]','Exposition Nicolas Marcone','','inherit','closed','closed','','92-revision-v1','','','2015-12-27 11:16:36','2015-12-27 10:16:36','',92,'http://2016.alessandro-chianese.com/2015/12/27/92-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(350,1,'2015-12-27 11:23:13','2015-12-27 10:23:13','[pdf-embedder url=\"http://2016.alessandro-chianese.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/Accrochages_n167_52p.pdf\"]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[pdf-embedder url=\"http://2016.alessandro-chianese.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/BULCOM-No.19-vendredi-15-mai-2015.pdf\"]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[pdf-embedder url=\"http://2016.alessandro-chianese.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/20140517EXPRESS.pdf\"]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[pdf-embedder url=\"http://2016.alessandro-chianese.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/201409accrochages1.pdf\"]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[pdf-embedder url=\"http://2016.alessandro-chianese.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/201406pharts.pdf\"]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[pdf-embedder url=\"http://2016.alessandro-chianese.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/201410pharts.pdf\"]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[pdf-embedder url=\"http://2016.alessandro-chianese.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/20140919BULCOM1.pdf\"]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[pdf-embedder url=\"http://2016.alessandro-chianese.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/Bulcom-n42-vendredi-14-novembre-2014.pdf\"]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[pdf-embedder url=\"http://2016.alessandro-chi